    <title>Cut the Wall - Coding Challenge</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container-fluid">
      <h1 class="display-1 d-flex align-items-center">
        <img src="favicon.svg" class="favicon">
        <span class="ml-2">Cut the Wall - Coding Challenge</span>
      </h1>
      <p>
        Draw a line in the middle of the wall that cuts the fewest number of bricks.
      </p>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label>Try it out (bidimensional matrix):</label>
            <textarea id="editor" class="form-control text-monospace" rows="10">{{ include 'algorithm/seed.json' }}</textarea>
            <span class="text-muted">
              The sum of units in each row should have the same result.
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
          <div class="mb-3">
            <label id="result"></label>
            <div class="wall-responsive">
              <div id="wall" class="wall"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h1 class="display-1">
        Solution
      </h1>

      <p>
        The logic I used to solve this challenge:

        <ol>
          <li>Look for the spaces between the bricks. The more the better.</li>
          <li>
            Follow the steps below when visiting each row:
            <ul>
              <li>Save the position of each space (sum the brick sizes).</li>
              <li>Count the number of spaces in that position.</li>
              <li>Whenever there are more spaces, save the current position.</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>When you complete the cycle, you will have the best result.</li>
        </ol>
      </p>

      <p>
        This logic can be implemented with 2 nested loops that result in an O(n2) complexity algorithm.
      </p>

      <pre><code class="hljs javascript">{{ include 'algorithm/v2.js' }}</code></pre>

      <p>
        The source code of this app is hosted on <a href="https://github.com/marxjmoura/big-o">GitHub</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/highlight.js/10.5.0/highlight.min.js"></script>
    <script src="algorithm/v2.js"></script>
